The paper deals with content-based image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves maximizing mutual information, which is a common approach in machine learning and information theory (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on image datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
